1. fork aider 
https://github.com/Aider-AI/aider
2. clone aider into local 
git clone https://github.com/naveen-kumar-dy/aider.git
set upstream  https://github.com/Aider-AI/aider.git

3. now make the relvant changes . (add version into init file ) 
4. create a virtual env 
python3 -m venv venv
source venv/bin/activate
pip install --upgrade pip setuptools wheel

5. install aider in editable developer mode / u can use this whenver you make any changes . 
pip install -e .

6.Run aider
aider
